{"tid":2020413,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"是日最佳活動－簽聯署！","createTime":"2020-05-17T04:53:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-17T05:54:33.000Z","uid":345458,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"f16a5988a059f06842a2dde4e6fe9b06ccd8f3b3","tid":2020413,"uid":345458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T04:53:16.000Z","msg":"【立會要初選 「三不投」聯署】：<br />\n<a href=\"http://legcopetition.wixsite.com/form\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flegcopetition.wixsite.com%2Fform&d=5MMtl3Q8rD8%2FKomM%2B8e61yC3g8rst4cc2NZsp7q1N1o%3D&h=eb5ee534\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">legcopetition.wixsite.com/form</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">「港島區、九龍東和九龍西採取「初選加棄選」雙軌制，初選無約束力。」</span><br />\n<br />\n議會戰線要35+ 就一定初選！<br />\n要過半本身已經好勉強，<br />\n上面果三個選區仍然未肯搞有約束力既初選，<br />\n而家每一席都好關鍵，冇就係冇，<br />\n只要有一區唔肯搞有約束力既初選，<br />\n就真係一齊成個陣營一齊團㓕。<br />\n<br />\n而我哋做到既就係透過施壓，<br />\n迫使佢哋聽從民意。<br />\n- - -<br />\n今日聯署最後一日，<br />\n暫時得四萬聯署，<br />\n我哋目標係十萬！<br />\n<br />\n見到呢個Post推咗上熱門先，<br />\n之後每人再開多個post講聯署，<br />\n我要成個熱門都係初選聯署！<br />\n<br />\n另外如果有tg channel admin/ig page admin<br />\n都幫手spread啦"},{"pid":"dbccade3d038305959c8aa0548d4e80f568de372","tid":2020413,"uid":41873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T04:53:39.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bebd6c2ece2d3c65b64cdabc914055e6d4cd7217","tid":2020413,"uid":41873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T04:53:57.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2455d218653a0ed8d08ef663ec6f6c617ac8edf","tid":2020413,"uid":41873